Usage:
  jax generate light NAME [directional|point|spot]

Generates a new light source with the specified type, which defaults to 'point'.

  - Directional: light shines the same direction for all objects
    Ex: sunlight
    
  - Point: light shines in all directions from a specific position
    Ex: candle
    
  - Spot: light projects in a cone shape from position in a specific direction
    Ex: flashlight

